{"word":"Damascus","slug":"damascus","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Damascus</b> <a href=\"#/H1833\">H1833</a><br/><a href=\"#/H1834\">H1834</a> <br/> An ancient city<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=15'>Gen 14:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=15&verse=2'>Gen 15:2</a><br/> Capital of Syria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=34'>1Ki 20:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=7&verse=8'>Isa 7:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=29'>Jer 49:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=47&verse=17'>Eze 47:17</a><br/> Laid under tribute to David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=6'>2Sa 8:6</a><br/> Besieged by Rezon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=11&verse=24'>1Ki 11:24</a><br/> Recovered by Jeroboam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=14&verse=28'>2Ki 14:28</a><br/> Taken by king of Assyria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=16&verse=9'>2Ki 16:9</a><br/> Walled<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=27'>Jer 49:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=11&verse=33'>2Co 11:33</a><br/> Garrisoned<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=11&verse=32'>2Co 11:32</a><br/> Luxury in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=3&verse=12'>Amo 3:12</a><br/> Paul's experiences in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=9'>Act 9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=22&verse=16'>Act 22:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=26&verse=20'>Act 26:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=11&verse=32'>2Co 11:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=48&chapter=1&verse=17'>Gal 1:17</a><br/> Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=8&verse=4'>Isa 8:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=17&verse=2'>Isa 17:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=49&verse=29'>Jer 49:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=3'>Amo 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=5'>Amo 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=9&verse=1'>Zec 9:1</a><br/> Wilderness of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=15'>1Ki 19:15</a><br/><a href='S:Syria'>Syria</a>"}]}